"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The veteran makes two longsword attacks. If it has a "
"shortsword drawn, it can also make a shortsword attack.    \n"
"**Longsword.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 7 (1d8 + 3) slashing damage, or 8 (1d10 + 3) slashing damage "
"if used with two hands.    \n"
"**Shortsword.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 6 (1d6 + 3) piercing damage.    \n"
"**Heavy Crossbow.** _Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +3 to hit, range 100/400 ft., "
"one target. _Hit:_ 6 (1d10 + 1) piercing damage.    \n"
